            <p>I gratefully thank your paper &#38; the writer of the Boston Literary Letter in <choice>
                    <abbr>Nov:</abbr>
                    <expan>November</expan>
                </choice> 10th's issue&#8212;I have never had more comforting words&#8212;so noble
                &#38; glowing in themselves &#38; in their bearing on other things than me &#38;
                mine&#8212;I wish this card conveyed to the writer of them<ptr target="syr.00029_n1"
                />&#8212;</p>
            <closer>
                <signed rend="right">Walt Whitman</signed>
            </closer>
